BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 705 Td (When emotions hit 8-10 intensity, use TIPP to calm your body FAST:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 680 Td (T - Temperature) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 90 664 Td (Hold ice cubes, splash cold water on face, or take a cold shower.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 90 650 Td (This activates the dive reflex and slows your heart rate.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 625 Td (I - Intense Exercise) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 90 609 Td (Run, do jumping jacks, or sprint up stairs for 5-10 minutes.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 90 595 Td (Burns off the adrenaline your body is producing.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 570 Td (P - Paced Breathing) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 90 554 Td (Breathe out LONGER than you breathe in \(in 4, out 6-8\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 90 540 Td (Activates your parasympathetic nervous system.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 515 Td (P - Paired Muscle Relaxation) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 90 499 Td (Tense each muscle group while breathing in, release while breathing out.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 90 485 Td (Tells your body: the danger has passed.) Tj ET
